3325.Name: 2022 Tom Jackson Cup
3325.Details:
The Mercer Paddle Tennis League renamed our end-of-season tournament to the Tom Jackson Cup in honor Thomas R. Jackson, a long time Pennington resident, dedicated sports enthusiast, and a paddle fanatic. Each year, the Mercer County paddle community honors Tom's legacy and love of paddle with a season ending tournament awarding the winner the Jackson Cup.

In addition to the Mercer Paddle Tennis League tournament, The Tom Jackson Fund has been created to support Hopewell Valley YMCA programs.  The fund’s raises money for the Y at through its annual Tom Jackson Champion Golf and Tennis Tournament.  It is a fantastic event, and we encourage everyone to sign up.  You can find out more at https://hvymca.org/.

Everyone will play at least two matches in the Jackson Cup.
